title: Johns Hopkins study finds risk of premature birth among mothers near Pa. fracking sites
text:
Published By: Pittsburgh Business News - Today 
A new study out of Johns Hopkins University suggests expectant mothers near fracking sites could be at risk of giving birth prematurely.
